      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="662-35AD">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-662-35AD-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-662-35AD-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-662-35AD-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">To the Author of the L<hi rend="small-caps">ONDON </hi>D<hi rend="small-caps">AILY </hi>P<hi rend="small-caps">OST</hi>. <lb/> <hi rend="italics">SIR</hi>, <lb/> <hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>HERE being no Mail, I fancy the Two following pieces of Dean Swift's, will be an agreeable Entertainment to your Readers; they are from the late Dublin Edition of his Works, so but in few Hands as yet. <lb/> Yours, <lb/> <note rend="flush right">A. B.</note></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-662-35AD-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-662-35AD-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-662-35AD-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">Written in the Year 1733.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-662-35AD-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-662-35AD-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-662-35AD-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1">By Dean S<hi rend="small-caps">WIFT</hi>.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-662-35AD-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">P</hi>OOR Ladies! though their Bus'ness be to play,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-35AD-line-2" n="2">'Tis hard they must be busy Night and Day:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-35AD-line-3" n="3">Why should they want the Privilege of Men,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-35AD-line-4" n="4">Nor take some small Diversions now and then?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-35AD-line-5" n="5">Had Women been the Makers of our Laws;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-35AD-line-6" n="6">(And why they were not, I can see no Cause;)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-35AD-line-7" n="7">The Men should slave at Cards from Morn to Night;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-35AD-line-8" n="8">And Female Pleasures be to read and write.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
